Description: Contains identifiers for auxiliary files associated with Nanostring GeoMx Spatial Profiling experiments.
DependsOn: Component, NanoStringGeoMxAuxiliaryFiles_id, Synapse ID of GeoMx DSP ROI Segment Annotation File, Synapse ID of GeoMx DSP PKC File, Synapse ID of GeoMx Lab Worksheet File, Synapse ID of GeoMx DSP Config File

Description: Unique row identifier, used as a primary key for record updates

Attribute: Synapse ID of GeoMx Lab Worksheet File
Description: Synapse ID(s) of Lab Worksheet Files output from the GeoMx DSP workflow. Multiple files are listed as comma separated values.

Attribute: Synapse ID of GeoMx DSP PKC File
Description: The Synapse ID(s) associated with the PKC mapping file for the assay. Multiple files are listed as comma separated values.

Attribute: Synapse ID of GeoMx DSP ROI Segment Annotation File
Description: Synapse ID(s) for ROI/AOI/Segmentation annotations in the GeoMx DSP experiment.

Attribute: Synapse ID of GeoMx DSP Config File
Description: Synapse ID of config.ini file generated by the GeoMx DSP workflow.
